comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, the offensive goaltending call on the floor was overturned.
[Detectable with stop watch] Bogut (DAL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) maintains legal guarding position on Barnes' (DAL) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Parker (MIL) sets the screen on Matthews (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Parker (MIL) makes contact with Barea's (DAL) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Terry (MIL) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Parker (MIL) knocks the ball away cleanly from Bogut (DAL).
Matthews (DAL) makes contact with Parker (MIL) that affects his SQBR on the drive to the basket.
[Observable in enhanced video] Dellavedova (MIL) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Monroe (MIL) dislodges Bogut (DAL) from his legal guarding position on his drive to the basket.
Bogut (DAL) briefly grabs Monroe's (MIL) jersey but it does not affect his FOM.
The contact from Bogut (DAL) does not affect Monroe's (MIL) ability to defend.
Monroe (MIL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Barnes (DAL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) takes more than the two allowed steps after the gather.
The loose ball contact initiated by Barnes (DAL) occurs after the game clock expires.
Bogut (DAL) sets the screen on Dellavedova (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Plumlee (MIL) makes incidental contact with Barea (DAL) that does not affect his SQBR.
Monroe (MIL) sets the screen on Matthews (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Matthews (DAL) makes contact with Teletovic (MIL) that affects his FOM away from the ball.
The contact from Finney-Smith (DAL) does not affect Antetokounmpo's (MIL) FOM on the inbound pass.
Bogut (DAL) cleanly knocks away Antetokounmpo's (MIL) dribble.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) touches the ball while he is standing OOB.
Parker (MIL) commits a take foul on Matthews (DAL).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental contact with Barnes (DAL) that does not affect his ability to complete the pass.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) cleanly knocks away the ball as Barea (DAL) attempts to make a pass. The follow through contact is marginal.
The ball was last touched by MIL.
Bogut (DAL) sets the screen on Teletovic (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Teletovic (MIL) commits a take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
Teletovic (MIL) sets the screen on Barea (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Barea (DAL) legally contests Dellavedova's (MIL) jump shot.
[Incidental or immaterial] Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with Barea (DAL) that affects his SQBR.
